General
All strings in program should be constants (ie no string in the actual code)
Every line of code written more than once should be pulled out into a function
Functions should usually be < 10 lines, MAX 20
Each function should at minimum have one line comment explaining what it does and input/output (data type) parameters

HTML
All styles should be written in LESS
Minimum number of (divs) HTML elements should be used
In a question between using margin/padding or an HTML element with height - use CSS

